  <h1 class="articleActual_point">We can’t fix it if we don't talk about it</h1>
  <p>An openness that’s the key because unless a sense of trust is established more victims will continue to live in silence. So, instead of living in denial others must be encouraged to speak up.</p><br>
  <p>A lone voice speaking out can start an avalanche of thousands which aren’t that easily ignored. Only then will justice indeed be served.</p> <br>


